      <section id="id7691848">
        <title>I SEE THE MOON - THE MOON SEES ME</title>
        <para id="id6297928">Just like the heart has scientific facts (a muscular organ which pumps blood throughout the body) as well as “emotional” connotations (love is housed in the heart), the moon has as well.</para>
        <para id="id8199494">Research the facts about the moon. </para>
        <list id="id8211615" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>This is not to be about the historical facts about the moon. </item>
