          <para id="id8193901"><emphasis effect="bold">Revere</emphasis> “every creature would <emphasis effect="bold">revere</emphasis> him.”</para>
          <para id="id8203383"><emphasis effect="bold">Elusive</emphasis> “The moon was <emphasis effect="bold">elusive</emphasis> for it did not always rise at the same time.” </para>
          <para id="id7195916"><emphasis effect="bold">Supple</emphasis> “…slim and curved and supple as a hunting-bow.”</para>
          <para id="id8211946"><emphasis effect="bold">Lithe</emphasis> “the new young moon was <emphasis effect="bold">lithe</emphasis> and swift..”</para>
          <para id="id8345642"><emphasis effect="bold">Stealthily</emphasis> “<emphasis effect="bold">Stealthily</emphasis> he crept down…”</para>
          <para id="id8212220"><emphasis effect="bold">Fragmented</emphasis> “… a great <emphasis effect="bold">fragmented</emphasis> light.”</para>
          <table id="id8210939" summary="">
