      <para id="id8215367">But the creatures were very <emphasis effect="bold">friendly</emphasis>. They took the women to their <emphasis effect="bold">home</emphasis>. They gave them some food. The women laughed when they saw the creatures eating. They used two <emphasis effect="bold">knives</emphasis> and two forks at once! They ate two different kinds of food at the same time. The space-women had brought some gifts from Earth. When they gave them to the creatures they were puzzled. The explorers had brought some gloves and some pullovers. The gloves were no use because the creatures only had <emphasis effect="bold">four</emphasis> fingers on each hand. The <emphasis effect="bold">pullovers</emphasis> were useless because all the creatures had four arms. </para>
